# Deep Linking Standards

This document defines patterns for implementing deep links, Universal Links (iOS), and App Links (Android) in mobile applications.

---

## Link Types

| Type | Platform | Use Case |
|------|----------|----------|
| Custom URL scheme | Both | Legacy; app-to-app |
| Universal Links | iOS | Web fallback, SEO |
| App Links | Android | Web fallback, SEO |
| Deferred deep links | Both | Install attribution |
| Firebase Dynamic Links | Both | Cross-platform (deprecated 2025) |

---

## Universal Links (iOS)

### Requirements

- [ ] Apple App Site Association (AASA) file hosted at `https://<domain>/.well-known/apple-app-site-association`
- [ ] AASA served with `application/json` content type
- [ ] HTTPS with valid certificate
- [ ] Associated domains entitlement in app (e.g., `applinks:example.com`)
- [ ] Handles links when app installed; falls back to web when not

### AASA Format

```json
{
  "applinks": {
    "apps": [],
    "details": [
      {
        "appID": "TEAMID.com.example.app",
        "paths": [
          "/products/*",
          "/orders/*",
          "/user/profile",
          "NOT /admin/*"
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

### Implementation Checklist

- [ ] AASA validated with Apple's validator
- [ ] `application(_:continue:restorationHandler:)` or `scene(_:continue:)` handles incoming URL
- [ ] Parse path and route to correct screen with context
- [ ] Handle case when app is not installed (web fallback)

---

## App Links (Android)

### Requirements

- [ ] Digital Asset Links file at `https://<domain>/.well-known/assetlinks.json`
- [ ] assetlinks.json includes app package and signing certificate fingerprint
- [ ] `android:autoVerify="true"` on intent-filter
- [ ] Handles links when app installed; falls back to web when not

### assetlinks.json Format

```json
[
  {
    "relation": ["delegate_permission/common.handle_all_urls"],
    "target": {
      "namespace": "android_app",
      "package_name": "com.example.app",
      "sha256_cert_fingerprints": [
        "AA:BB:CC:..."
      ]
    }
  }
]
```

### Implementation Checklist

- [ ] assetlinks.json validated with Google's statement list generator
- [ ] Intent filter in AndroidManifest for http/https
- [ ] `Activity` with `android:launchMode` appropriate for flow (singleTask for main)
- [ ] Handle `Intent` in `onNewIntent` for existing activity
- [ ] Verify link with `AppLinks.getAppLinkFromIntent(intent)` before handling

