## Checklist Summary

| Area | Required |
|------|----------|
| Universal Links (iOS) | AASA, entitlement, handler |
| App Links (Android) | assetlinks.json, intent filter, verification |
| Central router | Path parsing, validation |
| Web fallback | Same URL works in browser |
| Deferred links | If install attribution needed |
| Attribution | Documented, privacy-safe |
